【conda镜像加速-清华源】
1、镜像加速文章
https://blog.csdn.net/ignoreyou/article/details/103837860

# 2、conda配置清华源(!!!完全通过命令添加可能未有效添加，直接修改配置文件比较高效)
a.生成生成.condarc文件
conda config --set show_channel_urls yes
b. 修改~/.condarc文件，写入源文件
vim ~/.condarc
channels:
  - defaults
show_channel_urls: true
default_channels:
  - https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main
  - https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/free
  - https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/r
custom_channels:
  conda-forge: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
  msys2: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
  bioconda: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
  menpo: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
  pytorch: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
  simpleitk: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
c.查看实际配置
conda config --show


# 3、镜像查找
https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main/win-64/

# 3-1、离线安装
https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main/win-64/cudatoolkit-10.1.243-h74a9793_0.tar.bz2
conda install --offline cudatoolkit-10.1.243-h74a9793_0.tar.bz2
https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main/win-64/cudnn-7.6.5-cuda10.2_0.tar.bz2
conda install --offline cudnn-7.6.5-cuda10.2_0.tar.bz2
